Summary(pl):	Modu³ perla Alias
Name:		perl-Alias
Version:	2.32
Release:	4
License:	GPL
Group:		Development/Languages/Perl
Group(de):	Entwicklung/Sprachen/Perl
Group(pl):	Programowanie/Jêzyki/Perl
